name: Maneki Neko
description:
Maneki Neko by Deny

Maneki Neko literally means (cat waving) and is characterized by a cat sitting with one leg raised. ... Maneki Neko, also known as Lucky Cat, this talisman is very special for the Japanese to attract a lot of luck, protection, prosperity, happiness and health.

Original digital art created in 2021.
Dimensions 2483× 3510px, 300 DPI, png.
